    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/470670e36630d1c327f54d7370c074df.avif?t=1745937634\" width=520 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/622fe35ff57cfb32dd3cb5f562280812.webp?t=1745937634\" width=379 height=29 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食尸鬼 DLC 是备受嘉奖的洛夫克拉夫特式卡牌游戏《密教模拟器》的一款注重剧情的拓展包。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/f5815335c077381429a136a270b2f86f.avif?t=1745937634\" width=520 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/5888d75253aad0c5988ba2bccefae8d0.avif?t=1745937634\" width=520 height=269 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名名声扫地的灵媒。一间没有窗户的画廊。一瓶允许人赴许多宴席中的最后一场的灵药。一种无法拒绝的饥渴的折磨。所有这一切都映在悼歌诗人最温和的具名者——挽歌儿小姐那雪色的双眸中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挖掘坟地。亵渎墓穴。进食死者以了解他们的秘密或是纪念他们。安慰或背叛生者。在淡白至极的画作中令失落的司辰不朽。只是得小心，你得满足你的饥饿免得它在你体内生长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/a7bf7bcec2c6e3c0e9b945b78980dc1c.avif?t=1745937634\" width=520 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/57a347d3ad2769bad24c4c5ec930932d.avif?t=1745937634\" width=520 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食尸鬼 DLC 包括：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/adcf43c7329f82bc8a554968688ca8d9.webp?t=1745937634\" width=353 height=35 /></span>作为一名名声扫地的灵媒靠不光彩的事维生。与画作进行想象中的对话。为悼歌诗人的目的服务，虽然这也许会与其他司辰的利益冲突。寻找凄美的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/d1a4def9a6d76282bd450c5a1b57a06c.webp?t=1745937634\" width=353 height=35 /></span>成为一名冬之长生者，在骨白鸽的爪下永生不死，所向披靡。亦或败给生长于乌有的神灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/7d7b0ffe359fbab12f7441052c0aa61b.webp?t=1745937634\" width=353 height=35 /></span>寻找并掠盗墓地。进食更弱小的或是更强大的死者以学习他们的秘密。与生者分享那些秘密，或者将它们呈现在画布上。进食你追随者们的尸体，并从他们那些比较有趣的伤疤中额外学到东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/871900/extras/da95feb2c8fa32d575747fe4d4ba18cc.avif?t=1745937634\" width=520 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食尸鬼出身在游戏开始时随机出现，但如果你上一轮游戏是因恐惧而结束的话，它必定出现。</p>",
